Titolo: Rampage (2018 video game)

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Rampage is a 2018 arcade game available at Dave & Buster's and Hollywood Bowl based on the 2018 movie of the same name, serving as a reboot to the video game franchise. As in previous games, players take control of gigantic monsters trying to survive against onslaughts of military forces. Each level is completed when a particular city block is completely reduced to rubble. Developed by Raw Thrills, it also serves as a redemption game. Warner Bros. currently owns all rights to the property via their purchase of Midway Games.